WEBVTT

00:07.013 --> 00:10.085
You go to sleep, Nicky. I'm gonna
go downstairs and make sure...

00:10.253 --> 00:13.165
...that Geoffrey remembered
to put out some cookies for Santa.

00:13.373 --> 00:16.171
Don't eat too many, okay, Daddy?

00:18.093 --> 00:21.642
Daddy, can you tell me
about the four middle names?

00:21.973 --> 00:24.533
Come on, Nicky, you've heard
that story a hundred times.

00:24.733 --> 00:28.169
I know it,
but I forget a lot of it, please.

00:28.333 --> 00:31.803
Oh, all right. All right. Let me see.

00:31.973 --> 00:34.851
Most children have one middle name.

00:35.013 --> 00:38.323
But, you, my boy, have four.

00:38.493 --> 00:41.485
And it all began the night
before you were christened.

00:41.653 --> 00:44.213
Yes, a lot of things
were different back then.

00:44.533 --> 00:47.252
Say, Uncle Phil,
can I borrow 50 bucks, man?

00:47.773 --> 00:50.048
Of course, some things never change.

00:52.000 --> 00:58.074
